data.description: Very private, stunning log home on 22 acres w/a creek. Both primary & 2nd BR on main level have ensuite baths & walk-in closets. Bonus rm & office w/blt-in shelves upstairs along w/a lg loft overlooking the LR. Totally renovated dream kitchen & pantry: 8 burner gas stove w/dbl ovens & two additional electric wall ovens in pantry/utility room as well as a 2nd fridge! SS appliances include 2 refrigerators, wine fridge, microwave, & W/D. Total renovation of kitchen includes new cabinets, quartz counters & 10' island, farmhouse sink, subway tile, tile floor.  Bathrooms remodeled. Floors refinished, staircase renovated, railings replaced, new paint in & out.  Extra lg 3 car garage w/lg room above w/new paint & carpet. Tremendous wrap around deck w/improved access great for entertaining. 2 wired wkshops. Sealed crawlspace. Custom stone fireplace w/inset flat screen TV. Vaulted ceilings. Lots of light. Plenty of space for gardens, pets, horses & enjoying peace & quiet while being w/in 13 mi from heart of Hillsborough. No restrictions. Only 25 Mi to Chapel Hill or Durham. A truly exceptional property. High speed internet.
